<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Responding to curent and future problems associated with conventional heating systems, and keeping up to date with the latest cutting edge technology, we are Daikin approved and fully trained to design, install and maintain Daikin Altherma Air Source Heat Pumps.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Refcom<\/strong><br \/>In compliance with current regulation and in line with the F-Gas Regulation, for all businesses who install, maintain or service stationary refrigeration, air conditioning, heat pump (RAC) equipment that contains &#8220;F-gas&#8221; refrigerants to hold a Company Certificate issued by an appointed Company Certification Body. Alpha Air Conditioning UK Limited is F-gas certificated with REFCOM.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-25afef2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"25afef2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b83f7bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"b83f7bc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"960\" height=\"65\" src=\"https:\/\/www.alphaairuk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/air-conditioning-brands-footer-1-1-1.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-2662\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.alphaairuk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/air-conditioning-brands-footer-1-1-1.png 960w, https:\/\/www.alphaairuk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/air-conditioning-brands-footer-1-1-1-300x20.png 300w, https:\/\/www.alphaairuk.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/air-conditioning-brands-footer-1-1-1-768x52.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/di